node.text:
THIS is the next quesadilla you *need* to try! We're obsessed with @thepioneerwoman's jalapeño popper quesadilla 🤤

Get more recipes from Ree, Saturdays at 10a|9c and subscribe to @discoveryplus to stream more episodes of the show: https://links.discoveryplus.com/4cdOy0ieygb. #discoveryplus

Get the recipe: https://foodtv.com/2U8F7c5 (Head to our IGTV to get the clickable links!)

node.text:
Chakalaka — a spicy vegetable relish from South Africa — is a DREAM when piled onto a grilled cheese sandwich! In South Africa, grilled cheeses are typically made on an outdoor grill over open coals at a big barbecue (known as a braai)!⁠
⁠
Link in bio to watch the full episode of #HawaAtHome with @HawaHassan on our YouTube channel (and to find the recipe, too)!
